readable.content: a couple walking a white dog down a paved street A man and a woman walk with a white dog on a leash . A man walking a dog puts his arm around the shoulder of a woman with pink pants . A man , woman and dog walk down a paved road . The man is walking a white dog with one hand whilst resting his other hand on the shoulder of the woman with the pink backpack .
